Get real. Last night was the first burn I have been on in a while and we waited almost an HOUR for all the burners to get there. They had other things going on. They had just burned in a raid or were otherwise occupied. Who knows how long the dragon had been up before that. You saying that a mid level guild can't beat an hour mobilization time?<br>
<br>
The keystone kops could beat an hour. It turns out burners just <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> aren't</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> available 100% of the time to burn something at the drop of a hat.<br>
<br>
But you will disregard all this, and make more unfounded accusations that I am a farmer. Really I am one of the last people that anyone in their right minds would accuse of that.<br>
